                            "text": "%WolverineSimple%: They made the mistake of thinkin' they had me under control. It was a fatal mistake on their part.",
                            "response": {
                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                "line": {
                                    "text": "%PLAYER%: So you broke out of here?",
